Resources to learn Git and GitHub.

Getting started with excerpt's from the Odin Project.
Setup Git
https://www.theodinproject.com/lessons/foundations-setting-up-git
Intro to Git
https://www.theodinproject.com/lessons/foundations-introduction-to-git
Git Basics
https://www.theodinproject.com/lessons/foundations-git-basics
-The Odin Project is a full curriculum for learning web development, within it are great guides on how to get started with Git. These guides should work outside of the context of the curriculum.

How to Write Commit Messages
https://www.conventionalcommits.org/en/v1.0.0/
